, abdominal tergites; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[918,933,1729,1753]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">b</emphasis>
, terminalia, dorsal view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1209,1221,1729,1753]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">c</emphasis>
, ventromedial lobe, ventral view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[297,312,1761,1785]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">d</emphasis>
, sternite IX, ventral view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[597,609,1761,1785]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">e</emphasis>
, genitalia, ventral view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[874,883,1761,1785]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">f</emphasis>
, genitalia, lateral view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1140,1153,1761,1785]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">g</emphasis>
, gonarcus, posterior view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,166,1793,1817]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">h</emphasis>
, gonarcus, dorsal view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[428,527,1793,1817]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">female: i</emphasis>
, fertilization canal; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[744,753,1793,1817]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">j</emphasis>
, sternite VIII and posterior border of sternite VII, ventral view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,166,1825,1849]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">k</emphasis>
, spermatheca; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[332,339,1825,1849]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">l</emphasis>
, terminalia, lateral view. Gonarcal median lobe (gml); gonarcal lateral lobe (gll), membrane (mbn). Scale = 0.1 mm, except for 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[445,458,1857,1881]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">a</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
